title: Ep. 819 - Sleazy Democrat Gave The Kiss of Death
description:
Andrew Cuomo resigns in disgrace, a Republican senatorial candidate calls out anti-white racism, and YouTube censors Rand Paul—a medical doctor and U.S. Senator—for contradicting scientists and the government.
My new book ’Speechless: Controlling Words, Controlling Minds,’ is now available wherever books are sold. Grab your copy today here: https://utm.io/udtMJ
